Apply the regular expression : 
(?i)((^[aeiou])|(\s+[aeiou]))\w+?[aeiou]\b
to 

"Arline ate eight apples and one orange while Anita hadn't any"


This will find any words starting with vowels or spaces and vowels followed by any word character and vowel and the end of the word

Arline, ate, one, orange, Anita
